snippet.title: Hoku Shrine Game Trailer / Трейлер к игре Hoku Shrine
snippet.description:
I wanted to try my hand at being a game developer. Let's see how it turns out :) Here's the trailer.
The game page is already on the site on Steam, add it to your wishlist!
